<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p><strong>The <span class="title-main">Fungal Biology &amp; Ecology minor is being </span>discontinued. Contact the minor advisor for current class availability. </strong></p>
<p>The minor in Fungal Biology &amp; Ecology is for students interested in a concentrated exposure to and knowledge of the fungi and allied organisms.</p>
<p>The minor is sponsored by the <a href="/departments-programs-degrees/plant-pathology/">Plant Pathology Department</a>.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p><a href="mailto:grlandon@ucdavis.edu">Grace Gomez</a></p>
